00:49:07.027 --> 00:49:10.631 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Although the peninsula
was under colonial rule for some time

00:49:10.631 --> 00:49:13.600 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and has been involved in other military conflicts,

00:49:13.600 --> 00:49:17.771 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah’s Witnesses there 
have maintained their Christian neutrality

00:49:17.771 --> 00:49:20.574 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
by not taking sides.

00:49:20.574 --> 00:49:22.776 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
