in behalf of these faithful brothers.

00:49:34.321 --> 00:49:36.890 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In the future, we look forward

00:49:36.890 --> 00:49:40.060 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to even further relief
from fair-minded officials in this country.

00:49:41.461 --> 00:49:45.065 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This is the Ganseong Congregation.

00:49:45.065 --> 00:49:48.835 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Their territory has a population
of approximately 23,000

00:49:48.835 --> 00:49:51.138 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and is partially located

00:49:51.138 --> 00:49:53.840 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in the demilitarized zone
near the North Korean border.

00:49:55.108 --> 00:49:58.078 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s not uncommon for the almost 50 publishers

00:49:58.078 --> 00:50:00.714 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to conduct over 60 Bible studies each month.

00:50:01.515 --> 00:50:02.749 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In fact,

00:50:02.749 --> 00:50:07.387 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
some 30 publishers
—or 60 percent of the congregation—

00:50:07.387 --> 00:50:10.357 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
serve as regular pioneers.

00:50:10.357 --> 00:50:13.026 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Because of its location, many of the residents

00:50:13.026 --> 00:50:17.097 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
