are isolated from the rest of the country.

00:50:17.097 --> 00:50:19.099 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Our brothers and sisters

00:50:19.099 --> 00:50:22.569 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
often meet people who work for the military.

00:50:22.569 --> 00:50:25.806 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Because of the congregation’s proximity
to the border,

00:50:25.806 --> 00:50:29.142 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
