00:50:32.446 --> 00:50:35.816 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
To reach such visitors with the good news,
our brothers have organized

00:50:35.816 --> 00:50:39.453 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
public witnessing stands
in a number of locations.

00:50:39.453 --> 00:50:43.490 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We love our brothers and sisters
in the Ganseong Congregation very much.

00:50:44.925 --> 00:50:48.929 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And they send their love
to all of us around the world.

